Privacy Policies
EXXON MOBIL REWARDS+ PRIVACY STATEMENT  (“Privacy Statement”)
Effective as of 17 of March 2023
Exxon Mobil Rewards+ (“EM Rewards+”, “we” or “us”), a rewards program operated by ExxonMobil Oil Corporation, is committed to respecting your privacy. We want you to know how we may collect, use, share, keep, and safeguard information about you and the choices that are available to you as it relates to that information. Note that certain terms used in this Privacy Statement are defined below in Section 8.
This Privacy Statement applies to EM Rewards+, its website and any interaction between you and EM Rewards+ through apps, such as the Exxon Mobil Rewards+ mobile application (“EM Rewards+ App” or “App”) as well as your use or access of any EM Rewards+ online services or any content that links to this statement. It does not apply to those websites that have separate terms and conditions or online privacy statements, such as those of our Sponsors or other apps, websites or services offered by us or other members of the ExxonMobil Corporate Family.
EM Rewards+ is not intended for children under 13 years of age. We do not knowingly solicit data online from, or market online to, children under 13 years of age.
We may change this Privacy Statement from time to time, so we recommend that you check the current version available on a regular basis. If we make changes to this statement, we will update the “Effective Date” at the top of this page so that you know changes have been made.
This Privacy Statement describes how we and other entities that are connected to EM Rewards+, such as our Sponsors and Service Providers, may collect, use, share, keep, and safeguard information that we get about you online. It also describes how we may combine types of information (such as Online Information and Other Information) and how we then use the combined information. We gather Online Information if you:
Visit or use our websites or web services, including EM Rewards+ App;
Receive or reply to electronic communications from us;
View or click on our ads or other online content; and
Interact with us through social media websites and other websites and apps.
