When ExxonMobil relies on an individual’s consent as a legal basis to process personal data, individuals can withdraw their consent at any time. Visitors wishing to withdraw their consent should notify us at
data.privacy.office@exxonmobil.com
and we will stop the processing of your personal data as soon as reasonably possible.
